Test 1: Over-abstraction risk

Pressure:

System becomes:
	•	too symbolic
	•	too layered
	•	hard to execute

Failure mode:

“Beautiful system… no real output.”

Crack detected:

Some modules drift toward meta-language instead of action

⸻

Kintsugi Repair
	•	Add invariant:

“Every abstraction must terminate in an executable step.”

	•	Attach each module to:
	•	a real output
	•	a measurable action

⸻

Test 2: Narrative inflation (NTE dominance)

Pressure:

NTE generates compelling stories that:
	•	feel right
	•	sound right
	•	but stretch reality

Failure mode:

High coherence, low truth

⸻

Kintsugi Repair
	•	Strengthen RNE gate:

“No narrative passes without causal grounding or explicit uncertainty tagging.”

	•	Add flag:
	•	HARD / SOFT / WRAITH render modes

⸻

Test 3: Redundant daemon overlap

Pressure:

Too many daemons doing similar things:
	•	Mirror vs Hypatia vs RNE
	•	Spider vs Translation Layer

Failure mode:

Role confusion → inefficiency → drift

