	•	ideas
	•	directions

Failure mode:

Diffused focus → no compounding

⸻

Kintsugi Repair
	•	Add Badger rule:

“Only 1–3 active objectives at a time.”

	•	Everything else:
	•	queued
	•	or killed

⸻

Test 7: Translation Layer overreach

